// nth terms, special sequences, subscript notation); 9.2 Rational and
// irrational numbers (inc. recurring decimals → fractions); 9.3 Surds
// (simplify, +/-, ×/÷, rationalise); 9.4 Sets (notation, ∪/∩/⊂, Venn,
