      example: 'Data 3, 4, 6, 8, 8, 6, 6, 4, 7, 7, 7, 8, 11 (n=13). Sorted: 3 4 4 6 6 6 7 7 7 8 8 8 11. Position (13+1)/2 = 7. Median = 7.',
